quoteText: Provozovatel se zavazuje obsah E-mailů needitovat, necenzurovat a nemonitorovat, není-li v těchto Podmínkách stanoveno jinak.
title: The service does not index or open files that you upload

tosdr.case: The service does not index or open files that you upload
tosdr.tldr: The privacy policy states (in czech) that 'The Operator undertakes to ensure that the contents of the Emails will not be censored or monitored unless otherwise specified in these Terms.'
